node.title: Homicide investigation after death of Invercargill baby
node.description: The four-month-old was taken to hospital with critical injuries last Saturday and transferred to Auckland's Starship Hospital, where the infant died yesterday.
node.content:
["Homicide detectives are investigating the death of a baby from Invercargill.", "", "
The baby died at Auckland's Starship Hospital yesterday. Photo: RNZ / Claire Eastham-Farrelly
", "The four-month-old was taken to hospital with critical injuries last Saturday morning and transferred to Auckland's Starship Hospital, where the infant died yesterday.", "Police say they are still speaking to the people who live at a property in Elizabeth Street in Invercargill and are not seeking anyone else."]
